## Interface: 11508
## Title: LibCodex-1.0-ItemBonuses
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / ItemBonuses (Vanilla / Hardcore flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the ItemBonuses module. Per-module split keeps the core lib's bytecode pool tiny and lets consumers pay only for modules they query.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 1
## LoadOnDemand: 1
## Dependencies: LibCodex-1.0
## X-Curse-Project-ID: 1532131
## X-License: MIT

# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# ItemBonuses catalog for the Vanilla / Hardcore flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against ItemBonuses.

Data_Vanilla\ItemBonuses.lua
